[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0093","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0093.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0031","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer JavaScript 信息泄露漏洞","description":"JavaScript 同源策略绕过漏洞存在于 Internet Explorer 3.x/4.x 及 Netscape 2.x/3.x/4.x 等早期浏览器中。远程攻击者可通过在恶意网页中植入特制 JavaScript 代码，监控用户跨站点的网页浏览活动，窃取用户的浏览历史与访问行为等敏感信息。该漏洞由贝尔实验室发现并报告，CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级低，但由于浏览器版本较早且已停止支持，实际利用价值有限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0031"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:23.630","remediation":"立即停止使用 Internet Explorer 3.x/4.x 及 Netscape 2.x/3.x/4.x，升级到受支持的主流浏览器（如 Chrome、Edge、Firefox 最新版本），这些浏览器已不存在该跨域脚本监控漏洞。对于无法升级浏览器的老旧系统，建议在终端安装脚本拦截插件（如 NoScript）并禁用 JavaScript 执行作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.codetalker.com/advisories/vendor/hp/hpsbux9707-065.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0093.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0930","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0930.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0628","title":"GNU RWHO/rwhod 服务信息泄露漏洞","description":"rwho/rwhod 服务运行于 Unix/Linux 系统，基于 UDP 协议广播用户登录状态、系统运行时间等信息。该服务默认不进行身份认证，攻击者可在同一广播域内监听并收集目标系统的用户名、登录时长、终端类型等敏感信息，为后续针对性攻击提供情报支撑。此漏洞源于服务设计缺陷，影响所有启用了 rwho/rwhod 的类 Unix 系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。建议在无需使用该服务的环境中禁用或通过防火墙限制 UDP 端口 513 的访问。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0628"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:45.330","remediation":"建议立即停止并禁用 rwhod 服务：`systemctl stop rwhod && systemctl disable rwhod`（Systemd 系统）或 `service rwhod stop && chkconfig rwhod off`（SysV 系统）。如业务确实需要 rwhod 服务，应在防火墙层面限制 UDP 端口 513 仅允许受信任网段访问，并配置 hosts.{allow,deny} 白名单控制连接来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0628","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0628.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0628","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0628.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0628.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0628.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5fhh-rhpf-rxrp/GHSA-5fhh-rhpf-rxrp.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0628.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a257f052-36b0-4db1-9cd3-c865c04d3601.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0930.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0807","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0807.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0541","title":"Web 资源访问密码可猜测漏洞","description":"该漏洞是由于用于保护 WWW URL 访问的认证密码强度不足或使用常见弱口令，导致远程攻击者可通过字典猜解或暴力枚举方式获取有效密码，从而在未授权的情况下访问受保护的 Web 页面或资源。此类问题常见于 HTTP Basic Authentication 及 URL 嵌入式密码场景，攻击门槛低且影响范围广泛，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。修复措施包括使用高强度复杂密码、启用多因素认证及避免在 URL 中明文传递凭据。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0541"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:36.393","remediation":"对所有 Web 认证页面强制使用长度 ≥12 位、包含大小写字母数字及特殊字符的强密码，并实施账户锁定策略（连续 5 次失败锁定 30 分钟），同时启用多因素认证（MFA）并定期使用密码审计工具检查弱口令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0541"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0807.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0799","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0799.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0533","title":"DNS服务器反查询漏洞","description":"DNS 服务器存在反查询（Inverse Query）信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标 DNS 服务器发送特制的反查询请求，绕过正常访问控制获取内网主机名与 IP 地址对应关系等网络拓扑敏感信息。攻击者利用泄漏的信息可进一步实施针对性渗透攻击，扩大攻击面。该漏洞影响多种未禁用反查询功能的 DNS 服务器软件，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议禁用反查询功能或升级至不受影响的版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0533"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:35.763","remediation":"升级 DNS 服务器软件至最新受支持版本（如 BIND 升级至 9.16.x 或更高版本），并在 named.conf 中使用 allow-query 指令限制反向查询区域仅允许内部可信网络访问；同时设置 allow-recursion 为内部网络地址范围，禁止外部客户端发起递归查询。如使用 Microsoft DNS，升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本，在 DNS 控制台中限制区域传输与递归查询范围。此外在防火墙上限制 TCP/UDP 53 端口的来源 IP，仅允许已知 DNS 客户端和下游 DNS 服务器访问。临时缓解措施可关闭递归查询功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0533"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0799.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0798","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0798.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0532","title":"通用DNS服务区域传输漏洞","description":"DNS 区域传输（Zone Transfer）功能存在访问控制缺陷，未对请求来源进行身份验证和授权检查，远程攻击者可通过向目标 DNS 服务器发送 AXFR 请求获取该服务器管理的全部域名解析记录。攻击仅需目标 DNS 服务器未限制区域传输来源地址。成功利用后可泄露内部网络主机名、IP 地址映射等敏感信息，暴露网络拓扑结构，为后续渗透攻击提供信息支撑。该漏洞广泛影响未正确配置访问控制列表的 DNS 服务器（如 BIND、Microsoft DNS 等）。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0532"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:35.650","remediation":"在 DNS 服务器（BIND/Windows DNS）上配置区域传输（Zone Transfer）仅允许指定的授权从 DNS 服务器 IP，禁止对任意主机开放。具体操作为在 named.conf 中使用 `allow-transfer { 从服务器 IP; };` 或在 Windows DNS 管理器的\"区域传送\"选项卡中勾选\"只允许到下列服务器\"并添加授权 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0532","http://www.us-cert.gov/ncas/alerts/TA15-103A","https://github.com/websecnl/Bulk_CVE-1999-0532_Scanner","https://github.com/Rodney-O-C-Melby/dns-zone-transfer-test","https://github.com/SleepTheGod/dns-zone-audit"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0798.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0435","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0435.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0250","title":"Dan Bernstein Qmail SMTP 命令处理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Qmail 1.01 的 SMTP 组件在处理超长命令时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标服务器的 25 端口发送特制长 SMTP 命令，导致 qmail-smtpd 进程崩溃或异常终止，从而中断邮件服务。该漏洞影响 Dan Bernstein Qmail 1.01 版本，攻击复杂度低，且无需任何权限，可被用于阻断正常邮件收发功能。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0250"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:00.120","remediation":"立即升级至 Qmail 1.03 或更高版本，或在编译时添加 qmail-smtpd.c 中对输入行长度（LINE_MAX）的显式检查。如不便升级，可在 SMTP 服务前端部署流量过滤规则，限制单行 SMTP 命令长度不超过 512 字节。长期建议迁移至 Netqmail 补丁集（netqmail 1.06）以获得持续维护。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://cr.yp.to/qmail/venema.html","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602558319024&w=2","http://www.ornl.gov/its/archives/mailing-lists/qmail/1997/06/threads.html","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0250.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0250.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0250","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0250.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0250.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wq5m-pq24-j5cv/GHSA-wq5m-pq24-j5cv.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82079/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0250.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0435.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0407","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0407.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0219","title":"Cat Soft Serv-U FTP Server 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Cat Soft Serv-U FTP Server 2.5 存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞。已认证的远程攻击者可通过向 FTP 服务发送超长的 CWD（切换目录）或 LS（列出文件）命令触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Serv-U FTP Server 2.5 版本，攻击者只需拥有有效账号即可利用，无需其他特殊权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0219"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.290","remediation":"升级至 Serv-U 2.5a 或更高版本可修复此缓冲区溢出漏洞。当前最新版为 SolarWinds Serv-U 15.x，建议立即升级并开启自动更新。如无法升级，可在防火墙限制 FTP 端口（21/TCP）仅对可信来源开放，并禁用匿名用户写权限作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92574916930144&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92582581330282&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/269","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/205","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19218","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0219.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0219","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0219.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0219.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5495-52g6-8q95/GHSA-5495-52g6-8q95.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/F/ftp_servu_dos.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0219.json","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/ftp_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0407.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0377","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0377.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0195","title":"Sun RPC Portmapper 源IP地址欺骗拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.6.20.1 中的 RPC Portmapper 组件存在源 IP 地址验证缺陷，远程攻击者可通过伪造 127.0.0.1 等源 IP 地址向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求，实现注册/注销 RPC 服务或伪装合法 RPC 服务，导致目标系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Linux Kernel 2.6.20.1 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0195"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:53.223","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.6.20.1 以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本修复。使用 iptables 限制对 TCP/UDP 111 端口的访问来源，仅允许可信 IP 段连接 RPC portmapper。如不需要 RPC 服务，建议在 `/etc/init.d/` 中停止 portmap/rpcbind 服务并通过 `chkconfig portmap off` 禁止开机自启。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0195"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0377.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0367","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0367.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0184","title":"ISC BIND 动态DNS更新不当漏洞","description":"BIND DNS 服务器在编译时启用 -DALLOW_UPDATES 选项后，会允许未经验证的动态 DNS 更新请求。远程攻击者可利用该功能向目标服务器发送恶意动态更新数据包，从而篡改或添加 DNS 记录，导致域名解析劫持、流量重定向等严重后果。该漏洞影响多种 Unix/Linux 系统上运行的 BIND 服务，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0184"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:46.770","remediation":"重新编译 BIND 时移除 -DALLOW_UPDATES 编译选项以禁用动态更新功能；如业务需要动态 DNS 更新，请在 named.conf 中使用 allow-update ACL 限定仅允许信任网段（如 10.0.0.0/8）发起更新请求，并配置 TSIG 密钥签名认证确保更新来源合法性；同时升级至 BIND 9.x 或更高版本以获取完整的访问控制和身份验证机制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0184"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0367.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0318","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0318.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0153","title":"Microsoft Windows 3.11/95/NT NetBIOS 带外数据拒绝服务漏洞（WinNuke）","description":"Windows 95/NT 系统的 NetBIOS 协议实现存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统的 139 端口发送特制的 OOB（Out of Band）带外数据包，触发系统内存访问异常，导致目标系统蓝屏崩溃（BSOD），造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows 3.11/95/NT 3.5.1/NT 4.0 等早期版本，攻击无需认证，利用门槛极低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0153"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:42.847","remediation":"升级到 Windows 2000 及以上版本（WinNuke 攻击已在后续版本中修复）。若无法升级，在防火墙或路由器上阻止外部对 TCP 端口 139（NetBIOS Session Service）和 137（NetBIOS Name Service）的入站访问；在网络属性中解除「Microsoft 网络的文件和打印机共享」绑定以关闭 NetBIOS over TCP/IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1666","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20440","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0153.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0153","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0153.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0153.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0153.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g9jq-2w39-657g/GHSA-g9jq-2w39-657g.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/winnuke.nasl","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.194"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0318.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0310","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0310.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0150","title":"Perl fingerd 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Perl 实现的 fingerd 程序存在远程命令执行漏洞。由于 fingerd 在处理远程用户输入的查询参数时未经过滤直接传递给系统命令执行，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标主机的 finger 服务（tcp/79）发送特制请求，在目标系统上以 fingerd 运行权限执行任意命令，从而完全控制受影响主机。该漏洞影响多个 Unix 系统上使用 Perl 实现的 fingerd 程序，无需认证即可远程利用，危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0150"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:42.367","remediation":"立即停用并移除 finger 服务（该协议已过时），或升级到不受影响的版本。如必须运行 finger 服务，务必对用户输入进行严格的 shell 元字符过滤，避免将输入直接传递给 `system()`、`exec()`、反引号等命令执行函数；同时在防火墙层面阻止外部对 79/TCP 端口的访问作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0150"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0310.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0301","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0301.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0147","title":"Glimpse GlimpseHTTP/WebGlimpse aglimpse CGI 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"GlimpseHTTP 1.0/2.0 及 WebGlimpse 1.0 的 aglimpse CGI 组件中存在远程命令执行漏洞。攻击者可通过向该 CGI 程序发送特制的管道命令参数，利用服务器端对用户输入过滤不严的缺陷，在目标系统上以 Web 服务器进程权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响早期 GlimpseHTTP 及 WebGlimpse 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，无需认证即可远程触发。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0147"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:41.957","remediation":"立即停止使用 GlimpseHTTP/WebGlimpse，从 cgi-bin 目录中移除 aglimpse 可执行文件，并迁移至现代受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache/Nginx）。如无法立即迁移，可在 Web 服务器层面限制 aglimpse 脚本执行权限，设置仅授权 IP 可访问 cgi-bin 目录，同时移除不必要的 CGI 程序以减少攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0147","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20449","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0147.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0147","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0147.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0147.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0147.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j92f-fc3c-68gj/GHSA-j92f-fc3c-68gj.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/G/glimpse.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0147.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0301.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0301.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0301.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0252","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0252.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0111","title":"IBM AIX RIP v1 路由欺骗漏洞","description":"RIP v1 是一种距离向量路由协议，其设计缺陷在于未对路由更新报文进行身份认证，导致攻击者可通过伪造 RIP 广播报文向目标系统注入虚假路由条目。AIX 系统上运行的 RIP v1 服务存在欺骗漏洞，远程未认证攻击者可在同一广播域内发送精心构造的 RIP 响应报文，篡改目标主机的路由表，将流量重定向至攻击者控制的恶意节点，进而实现中间人攻击、信息窃取或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 AIX 系统上启用了 RIP v1 服务的配置，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0111"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.543","remediation":"建议升级支持 RIPv2 的路由软件以启用 MD5 认证，或迁移至 OSPF 等认证型路由协议；在边界路由器上配置被动接口并实施 RIP 路由过滤（distribute-list），仅允许与已知邻居通信，阻断伪造 RIP 路由更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0111"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0252.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0188","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0188.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0076","title":"WU wu-ftpd PASV命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"wu-ftpd 的 PASV 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标 FTP 服务器发送特制的 PASV 命令请求触发该漏洞，导致 wu-ftpd 进程崩溃并产生 core dump 文件。该漏洞影响早期版本的 wu-ftpd 服务程序，攻击者无需身份认证即可触发拒绝服务，在特定环境下可能进一步实现远程代码执行。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0076"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:31.463","remediation":"立即升级 wu-ftpd 至 2.6.2 或更高版本，该版本已修复 PASV 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法升级，可在 wu-ftpd 配置文件中限制 PASV 命令的使用范围，或在防火墙层面限制对 FTP 服务（端口 21）的访问来源 IP。鉴于 wu-ftpd 已停止维护，建议迁移至 vsftpd 或 ProFTPD 等仍在活跃维护的 FTP 服务器软件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0076"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0188.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0186","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0186.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0074","title":"Linux Kernel TCP 端口顺序分配欺骗漏洞","description":"Linux 内核 TCP 协议栈在分配监听端口时采用顺序递增方式，导致远程攻击者可通过预测后续端口号实施 TCP 会话劫持与 IP 欺骗攻击。该漏洞影响早期 Linux 内核版本，攻击者无需任何身份认证即可在未建立连接的条件下伪造 TCP 数据包，破坏通信完整性。后续内核版本改用了随机端口分配机制修复此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0074"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:31.197","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.0.40 或 2.2.27 及以上版本，这些版本已实现 RFC 1948 随机化 TCP 序列号机制。如无法升级，可通过 sysctl 启用 tcp_tw_reuse 和 tcp_syncookies 提升抗欺骗能力，并在网络边界配置 ACL 限制源地址伪造。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0074"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0186.toml"}]